# IT Products

## Difference between product, services and solutions

- Product is a IT software with a name, it is a GOOD or a SERVICE
- Solution - How to solve a particular problem with the given Product
  - solving industry specific need or business problem
  - akin use-cases
- Look at the website of IBM

## Fullstack Dev roles and responsibilities

When it comes to performance marketing, one of the biggest questions you can ask yourself
(or your advertiser) is what kind of conversion tracking protocol you want to use
1. pixel tracking or
    A pixel tracking is an HTML code snippet that is loaded when a user visits a website
    or opens an email. It is useful for tracking user behavior and conversions. 
    2. postback tracking.
